<!DOCTYPE html>

<hmtl lang = 'es'>
    <head>
        <meta charset = 'utf8'>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">       
        <!-- url_for() Flask-etik datorren zeozer da, fitxategiak kargatzeko-->
        <title>Νέμεσις</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <h1>Νέμεσις</h1>
        </header>

        <nav>       
            <ul>
                <li><a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/">Intro</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/cmdprompt">CMD Prompt</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/login">Login</a></li>     
                <!-- Honekin lortzen dugu gauden helbideari azkenean hau gehitzea, app-en definitu dugun beste zatira pasatzeko-->
                <!-- Ikusi behar dugu nola jarri goikoa politago -->
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <article>
            <h2>CMD Prompt</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Accusantium recusandae aliquid obcaecati. Sequi odit repellendus earum incidunt, 
                ex quo eos quae fugit voluptas deserunt voluptatem quibusdam consectetur. Voluptates, nesciunt sapiente.</p>
        </article>
        <article class='prompt'>
            <form action='http://127.0.0.1:5000/cmdprompt' method='POST'>
                <label for='cmd'>  ~ cmd: </label>
                <input type = 'text' name = '~ cmd' class='prompt_input' />
                <input type='submit' value='Submit' hidden/>
            </form>
        
            <!-- Hau da idatzi ditugun komandoak jartzeko -->
            {% if cmd_data%}
                <!--<p> executed: {{cmd_id}}</p>-->
                <p> {{message}}</p>
            {% endif %}

            {% if cmd_id and value == HELP %}
                {% block help %}{% endblock %}
            {% endif %}

            {% if error %}
                <p> An error has occurred: {{error}}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </article>
    </body>
</hmtl>